name: Verne Esca of A.R.M.A.S
description: One of Character for my Fantasy Apocalyptic Story "N.O.E.L - saga". Verne born as "Silent Orphan" and meet Az the leader of A.R.M.A.S in Far East of the "LAND" a very log time ago. One of the few people directly invited to join A.R.M.A.S when is built by Az as mercenary group and the wielder of one of Apocalypse Weapon "DEANDRA" that previously wield by Az.
